      "body" : "Both of therm outdated. There is a modern way too; it’s in <a href=\"https://stackoverflow.com/a/48038725/5772882\">the answer by Basil Bourque</a>. Also you aren’t contributing anything that isn’t already in several other answers. And when Joda-Time is asked for, suggesting the even longer outdated and notoriously troublesome <code>SimpleDateFormat</code> is <i>bad</i> in my most honest opinion."
