    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
    "body" : "<p>There are <strong>two ways</strong> this could be <strong>achieved</strong>.</p>\n\n<p><strong>DateTimeFormat</strong></p>\n\n<pre><code>DateTimeFormat.forPattern(\"dd/MM/yyyy HH:mm:ss\").parseDateTime(\"04/02/2011 20:27:05\");\n</code></pre>\n\n<p><strong>SimpleDateFormat</strong></p>\n\n<pre><code>        String dateValue = \"04/02/2011 20:27:05\";\n        SimpleDateFormat sdf = new SimpleDateFormat(\"dd/MM/yyyy HH:mm:ss\"); //  04/02/2011 20:27:05\n\n        Date date = sdf.parse(dateValue); // returns date object\n        System.out.println(date); // outputs: Fri Feb 04 20:27:05 IST 2011\n</code></pre>\n"
  } ],
